OL,6,FTests showed his blood had become
OL,7,Finfected with a bacteria found in the
OL,8,Fmouths of dogs and cats.
OL,10,FProsecutor Laura Broome told Carlise
OL,11,FCrown Court it was the pathologist's
OL,12,Fopinion "that this was passed into his
OL,13,Fbloodstream from the wound caused to
OL,14,Fhis little finger when bitten by the
OL,15,Fdog".
OL,17,FHawley admitted a charge of permitting
OL,18,Fa dog to cause injury while
OL,19,Fdangerously out of control, leading to
OL,20,FMr James' death.
